TSVAL: To compare the systemic exposure of ubrogepant following single-dose administration of to-be-marketed (TBM) and clinical trial (CT) tablet formulations of ubrogepant in healthy adult participants
To quantify the effect of a high-fat meal on the systemic exposure of ubrogepant following single-dose administration of TBM tablet formulation of ubrogepant in healthy adult participants
To evaluate secondary pharmacokinetic (PK) parameters of ubrogepant following administration of TBM and CT tablet formulations
To assess safety and tolerability of ubrogepant administered as TBM or CT tablet formulations

column12: Bioequivalence Study Comparing 2 Strengths of the To-Be-Marketed Tablet Formulation of Ubrogepant versus the Clinical Trial
